RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 37. Maiden Special Weight Purse 10780. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of Races Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: TOWN OF GUAYNABO pressed pace, led, driving. RAMWIL'S CHROME vied for lead, second best. DON DANY R. closed gap. EL MAJESTUOSO weakened. SYRIA MARIE trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 7F Dirt CR: 40. Claiming Purse 9016. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $27,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: LONDON GHOST close up, led, drew off. COQUETON held place. YADIEL M. off pace, short place. DAY BLUE vied for lead, weakened. LUCAS VONFEDAK dropped back.

WINNERS_DETAILS.BREEDER: Ocala Stud, Dr. William & Alice B.Russell & William J. Ter

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 7F Dirt CR: 31. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR FILLIES THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BELLEZA MORENA pressed pace, led, driving. MEDEGO off slowly, second best. CATCH THE PRINCESS close up, even finish. VINCENZA M mild rally, weakened. LADY RUNNER vied for lead, weakened. POWERFUL LADY trailed. PER RULING FROM THE PUERTO RICO RACING COMMISSION, BELLEZA MORENA WAS DISQUALIFIED FOR POSITIVE TEST.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6F Dirt CR: 84. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FREEDONIA led throughout. STRIKE LIGHTNING bit slow early, second best. KIMO close up, evenly. RYBOLT evenly. DON'T MAKE IT EASY chased, weakened. LIGHT OF THE WORLD failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 6F Dirt CR: 65. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON FOUR RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PLAYA INCLUSION steady attack, up. GONE SOUTH bid between horses, led, caught. OUR CHOICE set pace, grudgingly. CHEN'S CLEANSHADOW off pace, finished well. MAREMAR close up, weakened. SUCESORA middle of pack, no rally. FANTASY TALE close up, weakened. ANOTHERSONGNDANCE off slowly, improved position. MISS MAC dropped back. NIGHT CITY trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 6F Dirt CR: 52. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON FOUR RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CARTILLERO rallied, driving. MILO ALBERTO close up, bid, second best. RELOJ SUIZO seated rider start. RAFY Q. close up, gave way. EL FURIOSO AFY vied for lead, weakened. DESPERTAR BORICUA off slowly. QUE BUENO ES tight start, dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 26. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since December 22 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 7 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since November 7 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FLOR DE FUEGO led throughout. RECOMENDADA chased, second best. EMBLEMATICA close up, lacked punch. INNOVADORA failed to menace. LADY HELEN weakened. COLEGIACION failed to menace. NELLS PRINCESS dropped back.
